| [**Conditional Disaggregation**](/docs/design_docs/disagg_serving.md#conditional-disaggregation) | üöß   | üöß     | üöß           |
| [**KV-Aware Routing**](/docs/router/kv_cache_routing.md)                                    | ‚úÖ   | ‚úÖ     | ‚úÖ           |
